{"tid":830925,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港原創中世紀攻城策略board game  KS上線啦！～抽獎開彩！","createTime":"2018-09-21T13:42:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T23:09:45.000Z","uid":195137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4fcc91f5d181c5d387480354eaed9eab72afdbb9","tid":830925,"uid":195137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T13:42:20.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得一兩個月前我地出個post同giveaway活動，之前條link 係度: <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/747482/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/747482/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/821214/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/821214/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我地整左超過1年概board game 終於上Kickstarter啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nKS網址：<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1984279110/unrecorded-siege\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2F1984279110%2Funrecorded-siege&d=vs7F5PsZ8m7YXihqtHQyZTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=2e647077\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1984279110/unrecorded-siege</a></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/213031_81aa11acdcff011012de547d3040c20f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F213031_81aa11acdcff011012de547d3040c20f.jpg&h=40f643c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先係Trailer，第一次自已做影片，整得唔好求唔好插得咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VQUtfCt02Jw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVQUtfCt02Jw&d=vs7F5PsZ8m7YXihqtHQyZTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=df063215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VQUtfCt02Jw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《未聞圍城》是一個策略遊戲，故事講中世紀百年戰爭中，一段未被記錄的攻城戰。多元玩法，包括單人戰役，一打一攻城戰役，四人混戰及串連起超過十種以上戰役的傳承模式（Legacy），各有各的故事及勝利條件。而且，配合不同的戰役，場景設置，高低差更會有所改變！更詳細概玩法資料可以去之前個Post，或者上我地KS Link.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋晚上線，到依家進度已經超過50%了，求各位巴打幫手集氣，衝夠100%，等香港有多D原創boardgame. 我地真係好想可以帶到呢副心血俾大家。<br />\n<br />\n另外因為KS live唔夠2個鐘，我地文都未出得切已，&quot;早鳥指揮官收藏版&quot;(Early Bird Commander Collection pack)已經俾人搶晒，所以為左之前未收到通知概巴打們，特別會再開多一次，同樣限量30盒概早鳥版， 準時明晚 9月22號  8點追加。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/213221_84bbfdfae2f430d37e5730bf4ca9563d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F213221_84bbfdfae2f430d37e5730bf4ca9563d.jpg&h=dc3a92a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好，最後係公佈Giveaway抽獎。<br />\n經由Google公平公正公開概讚助<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/213539_5ebbeadab5607872683621689ce9c980.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F213539_5ebbeadab5607872683621689ce9c980.png&h=303526d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得獎者係：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">呃人man</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n已經引言通知左巴打，或者識佢概通知下佢。<br />\n巴打可以黎我地FB聯絡我地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKickstarter: <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1984279110/unrecorded-siege\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2F1984279110%2Funrecorded-siege&d=vs7F5PsZ8m7YXihqtHQyZTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=2e647077\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1984279110/unrecorded-siege</a><br />\n<br />\nFB:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UnreSiege/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUnreSiege%2F&d=vs7F5PsZ8m7YXihqtHQyZTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=872194f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UnreSiege/</a><br />\nIG：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/unresiege/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Funresiege%2F&d=vs7F5PsZ8m7YXihqtHQyZTANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=5a817a00\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/unresiege/</a>"},{"pid":"d1e5584983ee870cf003d33ea828595a45eda62a","tid":830925,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"c39aa1ddd41bcca15e5beeda76e47dfd92248781","tid":830925,"uid":195137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1e5584983ee870cf003d33ea828595a45eda62a","tid":830925,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:28:11.000Z","msg":"感謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8951961de33b6a0a8ce6ae3d11520fd079677f","tid":830925,"uid":184306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"我搶到早鳥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003eaa12b0a9b78f8d2b0ac0a6359255f0c044ea","tid":830925,"uid":195137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd8951961de33b6a0a8ce6ae3d11520fd079677f","tid":830925,"uid":184306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"我搶到早鳥呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T23:09:45.000Z","msg":"恭喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/